SpaceShip capable ForwardMove 
SpaceShip capable LeftRotate
SpaceShip capable RightRotate
SpaceShip capable RocketLaunch
SpaceShip capable CollectItem
SpaceShip capable BeDestroid

RocketLaunch include Shoot
ForwardMove include Move
LeftRotate include Rotate
RightRotate include Rotate

ForwardMove call FuelLose
BeDestroid call LeftWreckage
CheckCollision call GetDamage

Game must CheckCollision when ForwardMove
Game must IsDead
